<br />Hmmmm...
<br />
<br />I need some opinions then. Personally I don't wish to make any money from the project (hence setting up a charity donations link on the website). I don't  care and would actively encourage people to modify the code as long as it's not misrepresented. What I can't square in my head is that someone could sell for profit what I spent 6 months creating when I'm giving it away for free. Of course, a bit of text in a text file is not going to stop anyone but I'd least like to be able to distribute it with a clear message of what I, as the author of the work, deem allowable.
